{"tid":1074761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何文田游泳池天降抽風槽蓋擊中女泳客 男教練陪同送院","createTime":"2019-03-23T15:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T19:02:23.000Z","uid":42188,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6dd21fc1afbf2edf4e1a581f0fa045a1b0cef894","tid":1074761,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:35:57.000Z","msg":"昨晚8時許，一名姓林女泳客於何文田室內游泳池游水，其間一個2米乘2米的抽風槽蓋突然鬆脫，擊中事主頭部，在場的救生員見狀立即通知康文署職員，事主並在一名姓廖男教練的陪同下送院治理，警方經調查後將案件列作「有人意外受傷」。<br />\n<br />\n據知，當時林小姐正在池內上堂學游水，其間抽風槽蓋突然從高處跌下，直接拍落她的頭部。林小姐向《蘋果》表示，抽風槽蓋跌下時發出巨響，之後「個頭暈一暈，但就冇流血」，教練、救生員及康文署見狀，亦立即上前了解。<br />\n<br />\n據知，涉事的何文田游泳池已因「緊急維修」而暫停開放，直至另行通知為止。"},{"pid":"6665c8b0a2a7044b3ac55b210ab9bf78825b8d7d","tid":1074761,"uid":42188,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvKtEVe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvKtEVe.png&h=7f40d227&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7a0be2b4bed286891f05e53bddea6fe81301c58","tid":1074761,"uid":45232,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:38:27.000Z","msg":"一定係貪圖林婆婆既美色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2598e3b1809aed7b85d9357a5b96cf022cf99e76","tid":1074761,"uid":218556,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:48:51.000Z","msg":"睇錯中女泳客<br />\n心諗阿婆都叫中女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c721241e0f3f8942d5a292a7eab3541c12f68a45","tid":1074761,"uid":196329,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2598e3b1809aed7b85d9357a5b96cf022cf99e76","tid":1074761,"uid":218556,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:48:51.000Z","msg":"睇錯中女泳客<br />\n心諗阿婆都叫中女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T15:52:33.000Z","msg":"未入黎前<br />\n女泳客同男教練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\